{
    "title": "64 - Helping at the Church",
    "description": "دو نفر درباره کمک به خانواده‌های فقیر در کلیسا حرف می‌زنند.",
    "words": [
        "church",
        "poor",
        "smoke",
        "help",
        "food",
        "family",
        "kind",
        "cook"
    ],
    "Level": "A1",
    "estimatedDuration": 1,
    "sentences": [
        {
            "order": 0,
            "person": 1,
            "text": "Are you going to the church today?",
            "translation": "امروز به کلیسا می‌روی؟"
        },
        {
            "order": 1,
            "person": 2,
            "text": "Yes, we help poor families there.",
            "translation": "بله، آن‌جا به خانواده‌های فقیر کمک می‌کنیم."
        },
        {
            "order": 2,
            "person": 1,
            "text": "That is very kind.",
            "translation": "این خیلی مهربانانه است."
        },
        {
            "order": 3,
            "person": 2,
            "text": "We give them food and clothes.",
            "translation": "به آن‌ها غذا و لباس می‌دهیم."
        },
        {
            "order": 4,
            "person": 1,
            "text": "Do you smell smoke?",
            "translation": "بوی دود می‌آید؟"
        },
        {
            "order": 5,
            "person": 2,
            "text": "Yes, someone is cooking outside.",
            "translation": "بله، یک نفر بیرون آشپزی می‌کند."
        },
        {
            "order": 6,
            "person": 1,
            "text": "Oh, it is just the kitchen smoke.",
            "translation": "اوه، فقط دود آشپزخانه است."
        },
        {
            "order": 7,
            "person": 2,
            "text": "Good. I was worried about a fire.",
            "translation": "خوبه. نگران آتش‌سوزی شدم."
        },
        {
            "order": 8,
            "person": 1,
            "text": "The church helps many poor people.",
            "translation": "کلیسا به آدم‌های فقیر زیادی کمک می‌کند."
        },
        {
            "order": 9,
            "person": 2,
            "text": "I want to help too.",
            "translation": "من هم می‌خواهم کمک کنم."
        },
        {
            "order": 10,
            "person": 1,
            "text": "Great, come with me on Sunday.",
            "translation": "عالیه، یکشنبه با من بیا."
        },
        {
            "order": 11,
            "person": 2,
            "text": "Thank you, I will.",
            "translation": "ممنون، حتماً می‌آیم."
        }
    ]
}
